{"tid":1898600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《湊熱鬧、撩交拗》唔好再用「有無交稅」黎做有無份收一萬既指標","createTime":"2020-02-26T06:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T07:42:56.000Z","uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0332ec77170a732673d23744c3c537a36dff1eab","tid":1898600,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:56:47.000Z","msg":"稅收本來就係用黎資源再分配，「扶貧」、「津貼」、「資助」、「綜援」呢類安全網只係用黎確保社會能夠順利運作、減少社會動盪，係政府做得唔好先咁多爭議<br />\n<br />\n當然，政府「回水」係要有制度、指標<br />\n<br />\n但香港人一出世，就算自己無交過「直接稅」，但都付出緊「間接稅」，甚至父母都直接/間接咁交過稅；就算政府唔回水，都仲可以推好多措施覆蓋更多人、更多方面<br />\n<br />\n所以，要屌就屌政府亂洗大家既錢（社會資源），回水執行得咁差，仲夠膽講係「派錢」，莊閒都未分清楚<br />\n<br />\n呢樣就要屌普羅大眾仲停留響封建時代思維，覺得「官」比巿民大，難聽d講實際上「官」只係巿民隻狗"},{"pid":"a14996e467cbc06bf62d261fda803b65be131046","tid":1898600,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:57:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">響大家研究錢唔錢的時候<br />\n特衰政府已經清算手足</span><br />\nHA 清算罷工醫護<br />\n外媒記者報道<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Rt + like + reply</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/aaronmcn/status/1232553489743532032?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faaronmcn%2Fstatus%2F1232553489743532032%3Fs%3D21&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6Xz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=b23af4b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faaronmcn%2Fstatus%2F1232553489743532032%3Fs%3D21&h=f38fff00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/aaronmcn/status/1232553489743532032?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ezracheungtoto/status/1232556910894649345?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fezracheungtoto%2Fstatus%2F1232556910894649345%3Fs%3D21&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6Xz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=24d5ca2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fezracheungtoto%2Fstatus%2F1232556910894649345%3Fs%3D21&h=caebb208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.